294
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:43,189
Hentikan omong kosong itu dan pergilah.

295
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:44,695
Sakit, sial!

296
00:19:44,950 --> 00:19:46,179
Kakak bilang mau melihat-lihat kamar,

297
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,809
