Aku mau ke toilet.

330
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:06,945
Arlojimu bagus.

331
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,965
Kau menyukainya?

332
00:22:18,550 --> 00:22:19,705
Kalau begitu, aku permisi.

333
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:21,905
Kembali kemari.

334
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:27,405
Kenapa? Kakak mau mengomel apa kali ini?

335
00:22:28,230 --> 00:22:31,055
Jangan lupa makan
dan sering-seringlah membuka jendela.

336
00:22:32,370 --> 00:22:34,705
Jaga diri Kakak sendiri.
Jangan keseringan bergadang.

337
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:36,019
Pergilah.

338
00:22:36,020 --> 00:22:38,225
Jangan tinggalkan kakakku.

339
00:22:38,350 --> 00:22:39,889
Dia pria yang malang.

340
00:22:39,890 --> 00:22:42,219
