[ Astaga. Maaf. Haruskah kututup? ]

367
00:24:30,770 --> 00:24:32,445
Terkadang kau mudah tertipu.

368
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:34,329
Kau sungguh tak akan datang?

369
00:24:34,330 --> 00:24:36,749
[ Ya, dan itu yang membuatku khawatir. ]

370
00:24:36,750 --> 00:24:39,885
[ Bisakah kau menengahi
jika terjadi sesuatu? ]

371
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,085
[ Itu keahlianmu. ]

372
00:24:43,130 --> 00:24:45,729
Kenapa orang terus bilang aku pandai
dalam banyak hal?

373
00:24:45,730 --> 00:24:48,285
[ Baiklah, aku mengandalkanmu.
Terima kasih. ]

374
00:24:48,810 --> 00:24:50,045
[ Sampai jumpa. ]

375
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:55,985
Seolah-olah ada yang perlu dikhawatirkan.

376
00:24:59,410 --> 00:25:01,925
[ Universitas Myungil ]

377
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,745
Tidak perlu bersikap sok penting.

378
00:25:11,950 --> 00:25:13,145
Hye-ji, ayo makan malam.

379
00:25:13,360 --> 00:25:15,125
- Aku tidak lapar.
- Ayolah.

380
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,279
Hye-ji, ayolah.

381
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:20,315
