Penelitianmu sudah selesai?

416
00:26:54,910 --> 00:26:56,669
Apa itu penting sekarang?

417
00:26:56,670 --> 00:26:58,509
Minta maaflah, Berengsek!

418
00:26:58,510 --> 00:26:59,705
Jadi,

419
00:27:00,630 --> 00:27:01,949
kau belum mengerjakannya.

